{"tid":1438903,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"當你已經接受到以下嘅嘢，你可以選擇繼續做一隻港豬","createTime":"2019-08-10T02:41:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T14:55:39.000Z","uid":180154,"like":31,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d595d17c446206e52f4eb01ffe7231f94494adc2","tid":1438903,"uid":180154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T02:41:55.000Z","msg":"話說上嗰星期去左澳門玩，10年冇去過澳門嘅我發覺澳門已經變左好多。<br />\n<br />\n以前去澳門嘅時候，行賭場商場嘅時候你唔會有一種俗氣嘅感覺。依家通街都係大陸人，成個場你會有種透唔到氣嘅感覺，比起新城市海港城更加離譜。<br />\n<br />\n除左商場所有指示牌全部都係簡體字之外，依家連新酒店嘅發財車全部都係以簡體字標示，細心留意下10年前起嗰啲酒店發財車仲係會用繁體字標示。難聽啲講句，澳門係中澳融合呢方面已經去到一個冇得救嘅地步......<br />\n<br />\n去左兩日一夜嘅我已經覺得澳門已經唔再係我熟悉嘅澳門。如果大家覺得自己係一隻港豬嘅話，歡迎你地去澳門睇下，唔反抗嘅後果就係會咁......<br />\n<br />\n起我底嘅話你可以發現我以前都係一隻不問世事嘅港豬，但係今次嘅trip睇到嘅嘢真係令我好震撼<br />\n<br />\n今日澳門，明日香港，後日台灣。共勉之<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4b132d959dc2e05cd434674879bfebe0b7bbf55","tid":1438903,"uid":58089,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T02:43:29.000Z","msg":"5年前都係咁架啦 發現新大陸<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d494a1b4d12cf776232ac027f271f9c1005fb19","tid":1438903,"uid":241774,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T02:45:25.000Z","msg":"不思進取嘅後果"},{"pid":"ee3e25e336671f6be6af8f4616a6a9175be61c5b","tid":1438903,"uid":180154,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"c4b132d959dc2e05cd434674879bfebe0b7bbf55","tid":1438903,"uid":58089,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T02:43:29.000Z","msg":"5年前都係咁架啦 發現新大陸<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T02:45:56.000Z","msg":"依家先發覺自己以前做左一隻港豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccf90ac68e8f376f9ce03ce0840aae5543d6bf79","tid":1438903,"uid":269585,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:07:19.000Z","msg":"五年前佔中，我身邊就好多朋友問我<br />\n<br />\n&rdquo;其實你知唔知自己爭取緊乜野？&rdquo; <br />\n嗰副嘴臉我到今日都記得<br />\n然而<br />\n今日佢地都出黎反<br />\n<br />\n有心唔怕遲，慶幸大家今天都醒左"},{"pid":"de0add445d3fddb34f9049c98b47faff837f7663","tid":1438903,"uid":180154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:17:20.000Z","msg":"自推10連，希望多啲人睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"808a9df2a72c0a90599b89452d66f066a816d88b","tid":1438903,"uid":180154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:17:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ab2aea12a3f98c772f422a7034170d86563d4ecb","tid":1438903,"uid":180154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:17:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a19aab931982534f2fa015cb54f7cf98d3f279d1","tid":1438903,"uid":180154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:17:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7474272c8ea498a6ed11f1215b18e842c8a3c4a3","tid":1438903,"uid":180154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:18:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f50e3eb705bcf2692cfe5164b15fb3be374656c0","tid":1438903,"uid":180154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:18:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8ad4828eb7a471ca07179c526502e286b2118d4a","tid":1438903,"uid":180154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:18:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"037d7e32732640fbf39a1bcd8b40eb82da21fb8a","tid":1438903,"uid":180154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:19:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0eac39cddf6e9a97d834969a33879e79be9ce71e","tid":1438903,"uid":180154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:19:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3265c1821a9ef60502f3f1a8a6d5ee33fc0b99fb","tid":1438903,"uid":180154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:19:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cd1429928cee4533fcbaac51d257202251656c7a","tid":1438903,"uid":180154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:19:40.00